Reagan Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reagan_Wilson 0 Reagan Diana Wilson (born March 6, 1947) is an American model and actress who was Playboy magazine's Playmate of the Month for its October 1967 issue. Her centerfold was photographed by Ron Vogel.
